column1: Supplementary Data 1. Detailed list of differential eQTLs, i.e. variants with high posterior probability for presence of eQTL effect in high-grade cartilage (m>0.9) and low for presence in low-grade cartilage (m<0.1), or vice versa.

1 chromosome and position in GRC37/hg19.
2 reference allele.
3 alternative allele which is also the effect allele.
4 Meta-Tissue beta (effect size) for the given tissue.
5 METASOFT m-value for the given tissue.
